# Creating the GitHub repo

Primary reference: `skills/creating-github-repo/SKILL.md`

Use this rule for:

- repo creation under `unicore-railway` — **always private** (`gh repo create --private`); never `--public`
- the single `main` branch workflow — no feature branches, no pull requests, no GitHub Actions CI; Railway is the only deploy gate
- the commit message convention — Conventional Commits (`feat:` / `fix:` / `chore:` / `docs:`), imperative tense, one logical change per commit
